---
import { faqs, siteData } from '../data/siteData';
---

<section id="faq" class="py-20 bg-slate-800">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-yellow-500/10 border border-yellow-500/30 px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-4">
        <i class="ri-question-line text-yellow-500"></i>
        <span class="text-yellow-500 font-bold text-sm">가장 궁금해하시는 질문</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">자주 묻는 질문</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        궁금증을 해소하고 안심하고 서비스를 이용하세요
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      {faqs.map((faq, index) => (
        <details class="faq-item bg-slate-900 rounded-xl border border-slate-700 hover:border-yellow-500 transition-all group">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 pr-4">
              <span class="text-yellow-500 font-bold text-lg shrink-0">Q{index + 1}.</span>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">{faq.question}</h3>
            </div>
            <i class="faq-icon ri-arrow-down-s-line text-2xl text-yellow-500 transition-transform shrink-0"></i>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6">
            <div class="flex gap-4 pl-10">
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">{faq.answer}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </details>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-12">
      <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">더 궁금하신 사항이 있으신가요?</p>
      <a
        href={`tel:${siteData.phone}`}
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-yellow-500 hover:bg-yellow-400 text-slate-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg transition-all transform hover:scale-105"
      >
        <i class="ri-customer-service-2-line text-xl"></i>
        전화 상담하기
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  details summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .faq-item[open] .faq-icon {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .faq-item[open] {
    border-color: oklch(76% 0.15 85);
  }
</style>
